name: Workoutsathome
0:
”Alexa, open workouts at home for a random five minute workout”
”Alexa, open workouts at home and give me a random five minute workout”
”Alexa, open workouts at home for a ten minute workout”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: workouts at home
des:
The purpose of this skill is to allow someone who either works from home, or even a normal desk job, to get in small amounts of exercise throughout the day when time allows. You can either do a five minute or ten minute workout. All workouts, with the exception of the stair stepping workout, require no equipment. Each workout can be done in a small office environment with the exception of stair stepping and walking.

Ten Minute Workout Utterances:
- give me a workout I can do for ten minutes
- give me a workout I can do in ten minutes
- give me a ten minute workout
- for a random ten minute workout
- for a ten minute workout
- workouts for ten minutes
- give me a random ten minute workout
- random ten minute workout
- ten minute workout

Five Minute Workout Utterances:
- give me a workout I can do for five minutes
- give me a workout I can do in five minutes
- give me a five minute workout
- workout for five minutes
- random five minute workout
- five minute workout
- give me a five minute workout
- for a random five minute workout
- for a five minute workout
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
